## 🛠️ Tools & Technologies
| Category | Tool | Senior Logic |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Ingress** | Nginx | Single entry point, handling routing and SSL termination (local). |
| **Backend** | Laravel 12 | Using latest features (e.g., enhanced concurrency, better type safety). |
| **Frontend** | React 18 + Vite | Optimized build pipeline, modular architecture. |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL | Better for performance metrics and complex query analysis than MySQL/SQLite. |
| **Logging** | Monolog + Loki | Structured JSON logs with context-aware metadata (Request-ID, User-ID). |
| **Tracing** | OpenTelemetry | Vendor-neutral instrumentation. |

